==Demographics==
As of the [[2010 United States census|2010 census]],<ref>https://www.census.gov/# {{nonspecific|date=July 2022}}</ref> the population was 1,282 residents. By 2020, it had declined modestly to 1,244.<ref name="DecennialCensus">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/prod/www/decennial.html|title=Census of Population and Housing|publisher=Census.gov|accessdate=June 4, 2016}}</ref>

